Beijing Development ( Hong Kong )
Ltd. agreed to sell 163 million new shares to  Beijing
Enterprises Holdings Ltd. (392)  for HK$1.23 each, according to a
statement to the Hong Kong stock exchange.  Beijing Enterprises also agreed to buy HK$1.3 billion of
convertible bonds from Beijing Development, it said. Beijing
Enterprisesâ€™ stake in Beijing Development will rise to 54
percent from 43 percent after the subscription of the shares,
